sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / CI Pipeline
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant MutWH as Mutating Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS (self-signed)
    participant ValWH as Validating Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS (self-signed)
    participant Ctrl as SparkApplication Controller
    participant SparkSubmit as spark-submit<br/>(local exec)
    participant PodMutWH as Pod Mutating Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS (self-signed)
    participant Driver as Spark Driver Pod
    participant Executor as Spark Executor Pods

    Note over User,Executor: Flow 1: SparkApplication Submission

    User->>K8sAPI: POST SparkApplication CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / kubeconfig
    K8sAPI->>MutWH: POST /mutate-sparkapplication<br/>HTTPS/9443 TLS (self-signed)
    MutWH-->>K8sAPI: Mutated SparkApplication<br/>(defaults applied)
    K8sAPI->>ValWH: POST /validate-sparkapplication<br/>HTTPS/9443 TLS (self-signed)
    ValWH->>K8sAPI: GET ResourceQuotas (optional)<br/>HTTPS/443 ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>ValWH: ResourceQuota response
    ValWH-->>K8sAPI: Validation result
    K8sAPI-->>User: SparkApplication created

    Note over Ctrl,Executor: Controller Reconciliation

    K8sAPI->>Ctrl: Watch event: SparkApplication
    Ctrl->>SparkSubmit: Execute spark-submit<br/>(local process)
    SparkSubmit->>K8sAPI: Create Driver Pod<br/>HTTPS/443 ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI->>PodMutWH: POST /mutate--v1-pod<br/>HTTPS/9443 TLS (self-signed)
    PodMutWH-->>K8sAPI: Mutated Pod<br/>(volumes, env, sidecars,<br/>scheduling annotations)
    K8sAPI-->>SparkSubmit: Pod created
    Driver->>K8sAPI: Create Executor Pods<br/>HTTPS/443 ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI->>PodMutWH: POST /mutate--v1-pod<br/>HTTPS/9443 TLS (self-signed)
    PodMutWH-->>K8sAPI: Mutated Executor Pods
    Ctrl->>K8sAPI: Create UI Service (:4040)<br/>HTTPS/443 ServiceAccount Token
    Ctrl->>K8sAPI: Create Ingress (optional)<br/>HTTPS/443 ServiceAccount Token

    Note over User,Executor: Flow 2: ScheduledSparkApplication Cron

    participant SchedCtrl as Scheduled Controller

    SchedCtrl->>SchedCtrl: Clock check (in-process)
    SchedCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create SparkApplication<br/>HTTPS/443 ServiceAccount Token
    Note over K8sAPI,Executor: Triggers Flow 1 reconciliation

    Note over User,Executor: Flow 3: SparkConnect Session

    participant ConnCtrl as SparkConnect Controller
    participant ConnSvc as SparkConnect Service
    participant ConnServer as SparkConnect Server

    ConnCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Pod, Service, ConfigMap<br/>HTTPS/443 ServiceAccount Token
    User->>ConnSvc: gRPC Spark Connect<br/>15002/TCP (no encryption)
    ConnSvc->>ConnServer: Forward request
    ConnServer->>Executor: Spark RPC<br/>7078/TCP, 7079/TCP (no encryption)
